description: Erection of 9-storey building comprising 99 units of Extra Care Accommodation (Use Class C3(B)) with ancillary facilities, 754 square metres of Use Class A1/A3 Floorspace at ground floor, ancillary car parking and landscaping  and subject to a Deed of Agreement dated 15.01.2014 under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended.
